Thirdly, Iesus Christ is our The Church is a Mystical Body, the Head whereof is Christ.

Head. As a Body is either Natural or Politick; so a Head: And Christ is held forth in Scripture under both these Capacities. He is unto his Church a Natural Head, in regard of Influence; and a Politick Head, in regard of Government;


